Klasse PlayerInfo

java.lang.Object
viewmodel.PlayerInfo
public class PlayerInfo extends Object
Model class to hold the player's data for the info board.

    • PlayerInfo

      public PlayerInfo(int clientId, String playerName, String robotName, boolean isReady)
      Constructs a PlayerInfo instance.
      Parameter:
      clientId - The ID of the client.
      playerName - The name of the player.
      robotName - The name of the robot.
      isReady - The readiness status of the player.
